			     DNSSEC-Tools
			Is your domain secure?

This directory contains tools used for demonstrating the DNSSEC-Tools
programs.  The tools are described below.

autods
	This script watches rollerd status and simulates the publication
	of a zone's DS record whenever that zone reaches phase 6 of KSK
	rollover.

makezones
	This script creates a complete demo environment for DNSSEC-Tools.
		- A set of zones are created and signed.
		- A rollrec file is created to control rollover of those zones.
		- A demo script is created to run the demo.
		- A log file for makezones is created that shows the command
		  line and parameters used to create the demo environment.

phaser
	This script sets initial phasestart entries in demo rollrec files.
	It is used prior to running the demo.
